<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>memoryaccess&#95;def&#95;iterator llvm::MemoryAccess::defs&#95;begin ()</>}

For <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/memoryphi">MemoryPhi</a> nodes, this walks arguments. For MemoryUse/MemoryDef, this walks the defining access.
